__data__.text: This is Police Agent at 2025年02月13日（星期四）09:30 Plan：Wake up at 5；Have breakfast at 6:30；Start patrol duty at 7:00；Monitor crowd density and provide guidance during patrol；Support congested areas if needed during patrol；Take a short break for hydration and rest at 11:30；Have lunch at 12:00；Continue patrol and supervision of Chinatown corridors；Review incident reports and update duty plan at 17:00；Prepare for end-of-duty procedures at 18:30；Finish patrol and return to base at 19:00；Watch TV at 20:00
